\id TIT
\ide  UTF-8
\h Tito 
\toc1 Tito 
\toc2 Tito 
\toc3 tit 
\mt1 Tito  
\c 1
\p
\v 1 Paulo mitumi wang'wa Itunda hangi mutung'wa wang'wa Yesu Kilisto, kuuhueli wasagulwa ang'wi Tunda nuuhugu wa tai nuileta utaua.  
\v 2 Akole muuhuili wa upanga wa kale nakale sunga Itunda nisingawiligitya uteele aulagile kuupuma ikale.  
\v 3 Kumatungo yayo aulupimilye ulukani lakwe mu mbugulu aumpee une kutanatya. Aizepee kitumo ite kwilago lag'wi Itunda muguni witu.  
\v 4 Kung'wa Tito ng'wana watai muuhueli witu. Ukende nuuasilya, nuupolo kuupuma kung'wi Tunda tata nuukung'wa Yesu Kilisto muguni witu.  
\v 5 Konsoko eyii ite nikakuleka ku Krete, ingi umazipilye imakani ehi naakele kukonda nukuika ianyampala, akanisa kwa kila kisale anga nainukulagiye.  
\v 6 Munyampala nuuitekelo walekekutula wimelwa, mugoha wa musungu ung'wi, nukete eana ahueli neshanga itegwa kumakani nimabe hangi alekekutula agila anga adabu.  
\v 7 Ingi muhimu kumugozeeli, mu nyumba ang'wi Tunda, alekekutula nikimilwi. Azesinga muntu wiogo ang'wi singawigiilya. Singa wikaya kutaka walekekutula mugala ntule, aleke kutula muntu nuweta wilea, aleketula nsula.  
\v 8 Apagwainge: watule muntu musingeeli, mulowa numuzalazima atule muntu nuketi imahala nakondanei, nukete itai muuhueli wang'wi Tunda, nuuimila ung'wenso.  
\v 9 Nuhumile kemiila umanyisigwatai namanyisigwe, wahume kuapa nsula na munkolo kumanyisigwe, wahume kuapa nsula na munkolo kumanyisigwa nuuza, hange wakume kuanonelya ehi niakumugilya.  
\v 10 Kunsoko akule endu asukile nyuma, hangi awo niabadisigwe. Hangi nkani yaupungu. Niaputalya nakuatongela aintu muulimili.  
\v 11 Inonee kuagilya iantu anga nianso. Akumanyisa ayo nishanonee kunsailo aminyala, nukubipya eantu ao ehi.  
\v 12 Ung'wi ao muntu nukete mahala, wikalunga, Wakrete akote uteele nuugila mpelo, abi hangi ikale niitaki, akatahangi alaku.  
\v 13 Ingi inkazi yatai, ite gwa uagilye kungulu, ahume kutambula itai muhuueli.  
\v 14 Uewe ulekekihangwila mumahumo nisingaatai, akiyahudi ang'wi malago aantu, niisusha ikenyuma itai.  
\v 15 Kuawa ehi niaza, maintu ehi ni maza. Kuawa ehi niabe nawaga niagila uuhueli kutile nikiza. Kunsoko imasego ao nusinganilye wao wabipile.  
\v 16 Akulunga amumanyile Itunda, lakini kuntendo yao amuhitile. Nianso anyamilandu nishanga agombile. Nishangaahoiwe kuluka ni lehi nuluza.   
\c 2
\p
\v 1 Lakini uewe utambule aya nihugie nintambu ako nauhueli.  
\v 2 Ianyampala atule nuukepyi, heshima, busara uhueli nuuza muulowa nuugimya.  
\v 3 Uu uu niasungu nianyampala ikie muigeleki nuupolo anga antu nialangaie singa ategetani. Aleke kutula atugwa antule.  
\v 4 Inonee kumanyisa nimaza, kunsoko akuzepelya iananso kumahala nukualowa iagoha ao palong'we neana ao.  
\v 5 Inonee kuamanyisa kutula nimahala, ezeelo alangaile niaza mumato ao, hangi atule nuliijo kuagoha ao, ienso. Inonee kituma imakani aya kunsoko ulukani lang'wi Tunda lulekekutukilwa.  
\v 6 Kunkani zizozizo muaalye iahumba niagoha atule nimahala.  
\v 7 Kunzela yanyu yehi mieke unyenye kutula meingwi mumilimo nemeza, nukumanyisa, lagiilye kugomba nukukulya.  
\v 8 Mudue mumbugulu nekete uugenu ningila idoa, kunsoko ehi niakugilya ahung'we minyala kunsoko mugila nulube nulukutambulwa kung'wanyu.  
\v 9 Aatung'wa aite eakulu ao kukilakintu. Inonee kualoolya singa kilutania nienso.  
\v 10 Shangainonee kia, apagwa inonee kigeelya uhueli wihi nuuza, kuuite kenda inzela yao yehi anonelye umanyisigwa witu kukeela Itunda muguni witu.  
\v 11 Kunsoko u ukende nuang'wa Itunda wigeelekile ku antu ihi.  
\v 12 Ikumanyisa kuhita imakani nisinga ang'wi Tunda ninsula aunkumbigulu. Ikumanyisa kikie muupolo, mutai nimunzila ang'wi Tunda mumatungo aya.  
\v 13 Itungo nikusigiiye kusengilya uhueli witu nilekete uukende, uwigeeli wa ukulu wang'wi Tunda witu mukulu hangi muguni witu u Yesu Kilisto.  
\v 14 U Yesu aiwipumilye ung'wenso kunsoko itu, kunsoko akuleepilye kupuma mumilandu, nuukutenda kielu kunsoko akwe, antu niagombigwe niakete insula akituma milimo nimiza.  
\v 15 Matambule nukumasingilya imakani aya, akenela kunguluyehi. Uleke kugomba muntu uuihi wakumele.   
\c 3
\p
\v 1 Uakimbushe kusima kuatongeeli, uhumi kugomba, nukutula tayali kumulimo wihi nuuza.  
\v 2 Uakimbushe alekekumutendela muntu wihi nimabi inege nukibisha, aape elyoma iantu niangiza kitu uulamuli kulagilya kusima kuantu ehi.  
\v 3 Kuite nusese aikukite masigo mabi hangi aikilugoha. Aikukole muulimeli, aekatendile kiatungwa kunsula yiolu niyawidesi. Aikikae muwilu nuubi aikabepilye nukibepelwa.  
\v 4 Kunsoko amatungo akuaisiligwa ni Tunda muguni witu nuulowa wakwe kuantu wikigeela,  
\v 5 singae kuntendo yitu niyatai niaikitumile, inge aukugunile kuukende wakwe. Aukugunile kwakuoja kwakuutuga hangi nukuutenda hangi keapya kung'wang'welu.  
\v 6 Itunda wamulagile ung'waung'welu kuudu kunsoko itu kukiila Yesu Kilisto muguni witu.  
\v 7 Aie witumile eti kunsoko, kuaiiligwe tai, kuukende wakwe, kutule palungwi muupanga wa tai nuwakalenakale.  
\v 8 Ulu inge lukani la uhueli. Nimutakile mumatambule kwa ngulu wihi inkani izi, kunsoko awa niamuhuiee Itunda atule nimasego, nsoko amilemo nimiza naumiikile tongela ao. Makani aya maza hange akete nsailo kuantuehi.  
\v 9 Inge minege nuudui nuupungu, nanasoba wikungumi, nimigongano, nimalago. Makani nanso magila anga ndogoelyo sunga insailo.  
\v 10 Muhiti wihi nukumuletekelyo wisapatilyi mung'wanywu. Baada akuahugula ung'we kang'wi abiile,  
\v 11 mulinge inge iantu niihanganga ite, amilekile itai hangi mutuma milandu ikinyamilimo ung'wenso.  
\v 12 Niinikamutuma kung'wako Alitemi ang'wi Tikiko, kawize kunu kung'waane. Nikopoli inge nagomba kikie mumatungo ampepo.  
\v 13 Kaya umutume Zena mutaalamu kumalago no Apolo, kuhita kuhiilwa nikintu.  
\v 14 Iantu itu inonee amanye kidumilya mumilimo mumilimo nimiza nukukimbusha muula alekekutula alekekutula akuite gwa alekekutula shanga ituga inkali.  
\v 15 Ehi mahole palung'wi nunene akulamusha. Alamushe niakuloilwe muhuili.   